    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "tea and books don't change the fact that the pain is constant. it's not just sadness, it's this overwhelming urge to just... stop. like, if I could just turn everything off and not have to wake up to this emptiness tomorrow, wouldn't that be better than this endless cycle of hurting? it feels like the only real way to find any peace is to just stop being here.",
